        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:230:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/363/448",
        "text": [
          "٣٦٣. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مِنَ الْخُرْقِ الْمُعَاجَلَةُ قَبْلَ الْإِمْكَانِ، وَالْأَنَاةُ بَعْدَ الْفُرْصَةِ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "363. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: To make haste before the proper time or to delay after a proper opportunity, in either case is folly."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
